name: KeepSocialDistance
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: social distance keep
des:
When you say the social distance between people in feet, show its image on the screen. 
This skill can be used on devices with screens.

How to call: Alexa, open social distance keep
Set social distance (example): 5 feet
Return to the launch state: reset
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
